        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Dyson Airstrait 氣流直髮器抵港，無發熱板直髮、免加熱 set 頭</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/dyson-airstrait/pretty01/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dyson-airstrait</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/dyson-airstrait/pretty01/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 06:00:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[扮靚科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dyson]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dyson Airstrait]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221927</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div><p>早前 Dyson Airstrait <span lang="ZH-TW">氣流直髮器首先在美國、加拿大等地推出，等了半年有多，終於到香港推出了。</span>利用空氣吹乾並拉直濕髮，不倚靠加熱面板，讓髮絲免受熱力損害。這款全新造型器專為多種髮質而設，能夠塑造出具動感的豐盈自然直髮造型，同時保持髮絲強韌健康， 觸感順滑。直髮器兩臂夾着髮束，向下吹出角度精準的刀片狀高壓氣流並吹進髮絲。</p></div><div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221930 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot20240229at-4-694x427.png" alt="" width="694" height="427" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot20240229at-4-694x427.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot20240229at-4.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Dyson Airstrait <span lang="ZH-TW">氣流直髮器售價為 <span lang="X-NONE">HK3,980</span></span></p></div><div><h2><span lang="ZH-TW">釋放出精準氣流</span></h2></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">直髮器上有兩個</span> 1.5 <span lang="ZH-TW">毫米的細孔，加速放出氣流，形成兩排高速氣流刀片，以</span> 45 <span lang="ZH-TW">度向下吹出，匯聚形成</span><span lang="ZH-TW">一股集中的氣流，同時吹乾及拉直髮絲，容易操控。</span></p></div><div><h2>Dyson Hyperdymium<span lang="ZH-TW">摩打</span></h2></div><div><p>Dyson Airstrait <span lang="ZH-TW">氣流直髮器配備</span> Hyperdymium <span lang="ZH-TW">摩打</span><span lang="ZH-TW">。摩打輕量小巧但動力強勁，所產生的氣流足以同時吹乾並拉直濕髮。</span>13 <span lang="ZH-TW">片葉輪的轉速高達每</span><span lang="ZH-TW">分鐘</span> 106,000 <span lang="ZH-TW">轉，每秒可推送出超過</span> 11.9 <span lang="ZH-TW">升空氣，產生高達</span> 3.5kPa <span lang="ZH-TW">氣壓，強度足夠在吹乾頭髮同時拉</span><span lang="ZH-TW">直髮絲。摩打體積小巧，僅</span> 27 <span lang="ZH-TW">毫米。</span></p></div><div></div><div><br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/10/dyson-supersonic-r/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Dyson Supersonic r 全新設計風筒  「r」形機身按鈕設計更適合專業人士</a></li></blockquote><p></p><h2><strong><span lang="ZH-TW">智能熱控技術</span></strong></h2></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">與</span> Dyson <span lang="ZH-TW">頭髮護理系列其他產品一樣，</span>Dyson Airstrait <span lang="ZH-TW">氣流直髮器具備智能熱控功能。由玻璃珠組成的</span><span lang="ZH-TW">熱敏電阻每秒量度氣流温度</span> 16 <span lang="ZH-TW">次，避免極端高温傷害頭髮，保護髮絲的自然光澤。而所得數據會發送至</span><span lang="ZH-TW">微處理器，調節加熱元件，確保氣流不會高於所需温度。</span></p></div><div></div><div><h2><span lang="ZH-TW">兩種塑型模式</span><span lang="ZH-TW">控制温度</span></h2></div><div><p>Dyson Airstrait <span lang="ZH-TW">氣流直髮器設有「濕髮」和「乾髮」兩種造型模式，以及「冷風」模式固定造型。「濕髮」、「乾髮」造型模式均預設特定熱力及氣流，以達至最佳效果。「濕髮」造型模式提供三種熱力選擇，</span><span lang="ZH-TW">分別為</span> 80°C (175°F)<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>110°C (230°F) <span lang="ZH-TW">及</span> 140°C (285°F)<span lang="ZH-TW">。「乾髮」造型模式則設</span> 120°C (250°F) <span lang="ZH-TW">或</span> 140°C (285°F)<span lang="ZH-TW">，亦可進一步選擇「加強」模式。氣流控制方面，直髮器設有低速及高速兩種氣流速度選擇，以</span><span lang="ZH-TW">及冷風及吹乾髮根模式。</span></p></div><div></div><div><p>Dyson Airstrait <span lang="ZH-TW">氣流直髮器現已於</span><span lang="ZH-TW">香港有售，售價為 </span><span lang="X-NONE">HK3,980</span><span lang="ZH-TW">。</span></p></div><div></div><div></div><p><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/10/dyson-supersonic-r/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Dyson Supersonic r 全新設計風筒  「r」形機身按鈕設計更適合專業人士</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/dyson-airstrait/pretty01/">Dyson Airstrait 氣流直髮器抵港，無發熱板直髮、免加熱 set 頭</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/dyson-airstrait/pretty01/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Google 修改 Wear OS   進一步改善電池續航力</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/wear-os-co-processor-improve-battery-life-galaxy-smartwatch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wear-os-co-processor-improve-battery-life-galaxy-smartwatch</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/wear-os-co-processor-improve-battery-life-galaxy-smartwatch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美鳳]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 05:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手錶]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Wear OS]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221978</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>現時大部分 Wear OS 智能手錶的電池續航時間只有一至兩天，需要更長續航力的用户，可能需要考慮運動手環或搭載自家操作系統但功能稍遜的智能手錶。為瞭解決這個問題，Google 現正嘗試對 Wear OS 作針對性的修改，將處理通知的工作交由智能手錶內的協同處理器負責。</p><p><span id="more-1221978"></span></p><p>數年前，Wear OS 引入了 MCU 超低功耗協同處理器的支持，心率追蹤和步數計等較小的任務都交由協同處理器處理。現在，Google 進一步容許 MCU 處理從智能手機發送的訊息通知、回覆通知和清除通知等任務。這項轉變的好處是 MCU 處理健康追蹤和所有通知的時候，手錶的處理器能夠保持休眠狀態，讓電耗得以降低，從而將電池續航力延長。</p><p>日前發表的 OnePlus Watch 2 是首款採用此新功能的 Wear OS 智能手錶，廠方宣稱續航力可達 100 小時。以往 Wear OS 有不少為人詬病的缺點，隨著 Google 和 Samsung 宣佈合作並開發 Wear OS 3 之後，就有了大幅度的改善。Google 亦著手對該系統進行不少改進，吸引了小米、OPPO 和 OnePlus 等品牌加入，不過一直使用 Wear OS 推出智能手錶的鐘錶品牌 Fossil，早前則確認退出智能手錶市場。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.sammobile.com/news/wear-os-co-processor-improve-battery-life-galaxy-smartwatch/">sammobile</a></p><p>&nbsp;<br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/oneplus-watch-2-wear-os/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">OnePlus Watch 2 發表，改用 Wear OS 定價約 2,348 港元</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/29/fossil-wear-os-smartwatch-business-exit/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Fossil 專注傳統鐘錶產品，宣佈撤出 Wear OS 智能手錶市場</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/samsung-google-reportedly-testing-wear-os-5/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Wear OS 5 傳今年推出   Galaxy Watch 7 系列或率先預載</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/wear-os-co-processor-improve-battery-life-galaxy-smartwatch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/">Google 修改 Wear OS   進一步改善電池續航力</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
